SUMMARY:Last Saturday Storytime + Play at Literacy Kid Lounge + Bookshop
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a new storytime series: Last Saturday Storytime! \nEvery last Saturday of the month we will gather for stories and play at the Literacy Kid Lounge + Bookshop. This is the perfect opportunity for families who cannot attend a regular playgroup but still want to enjoy a storytime together. \nAt our March storytime\, Ivy the Owl will make a special visit to join the fun and listen to stories with us.* \nMembers: $18 \nNon Members: $15 \n*Ivy the Owl is a character from Ivy Brook Academy in Tigard. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/last-saturday-storytime-play-at-literacy-kid-lounge-bookshop/
LOCATION:Literacy Kid Lounge\, 2200 SE Oak Grove Blvd\, Oak Grove\, OR\, 97267\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts/Crafts,Books/Library,Family Fun,Inclusive,Indoor,Kids Calendar,Storytime
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Storytime-Saturday-Instagram-Post-Square.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Literacy Lady PDX":MAILTO:Sarah@literacyladypdx.com
