SUMMARY:The Magic of Spring: Planting Seeds & Creativity
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the first day of spring with storytime\, creative art\, and planting seeds to take home—let’s grow together! \n\n\n\n\n🌷 First Day of Spring Celebration at Little Nestlings! 🌼 \nCelebrate the arrival of spring with storytime\, creative art\, and hands-on planting fun! \n📖 Storytime: We’ll read The Tiny Seed by Eric Carle\, exploring growth\, change\, and the wonders of nature. \n🎨 Spring-Themed Art Exploration: Children will engage in open-ended art activities\, creating nature-inspired projects with seeds\, flowers\, and other natural materials. \n🌱 Planting Seeds: Each child will plant a seed in a small pot to take home and nurture\, connecting with the life cycle of plants. \nThis event is free and open to all families—come celebrate spring’s magic with us! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/the-magic-of-spring-planting-seeds-creativity/
LOCATION:Little Nestlings Early Learning Center\, 19200 Willamette Drive\, West Linn\, O\, 97068\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts/Crafts,Kids Calendar,Storytime
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Magic-of-Spring-4.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Little Nestlings Early Learning Center":MAILTO:colleen.littlenestlings@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
