SUMMARY:Sensory-Friendly Easter Egg Hunt in Camas
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a sensory friendly Easter egg hunt for those with special needs and their family and friends. Take a picture with the Easter bunny and enjoy a sweet treat after you hunt for eggs. RAIN OR SHINE. \nEgg hunt starts promptly at 10 AM. There will be multiple areas so you can spread out. There will be areas for wheelchair access\, visually impaired and preschool aged.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/sensory-friendly-easter-egg-hunt-in-camas/
LOCATION:Prune Hill Elementary\, 1601 NW Tidland St.\, Camas\, Washington
CATEGORIES:Easter,Inclusive,Kids Calendar
