DESCRIPTION:Go to Helvetia Farm Market for a fun\, family-friendly day featuring local makers and small businesses\, delicious ham samples\, hands-on kids’ Easter crafts\, and food trucks serving up lunch. \nBring your friends\, bring the kids\, and come celebrate Easter with good food\, great vendors\, and community.
