SUMMARY:Open Saturday at Pearson Field Education Center
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Open Saturday at Education Center on Pearson Field in Vancouver\, WA! \nJoin us on Saturdays from 10am-3pm for a day of STEAM education through aviation. Our center is perfect for youth of all ages to experience hands-on learning and exploration. \nExplore our flight simulator lab featuring Kerbal Space Program and Microsoft Flight Simulator\, a vertical wind table\, and historic airplanes and collections on display. Our various educational programs are designed to spark curiosity and encourage discovery. \nAdmission is free for all ages\, making this a perfect outing for families\, school groups\, and community organizations. \nPlease note that children must be accompanied by an adult when attending Open Saturday. \nFor any questions\, please call 360-694-5578. We can’t wait to see you there!
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/open-saturday-at-pearson-field-education-center-2/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Pearson Field Education Center\, 201 A E Reserve St\, Vacouver\, WA\, 98661\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts/Crafts,Educational,Indoor,Kids Calendar,STEM
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/PFEC-Interior-scaled.jpg
GEO:45.6226077;-122.6541186
