SUMMARY:Egg Hunt at Christ United Methodist Church
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a fun\, free community Egg Hunt at Christ United Methodist Church on March 28! Bring your baskets and invite your neighbors for a morning of egg hunting\, smiles\, and springtime fun for kids and families in the Cedar Mill community. There will also be arts and crafts\, prizes and snacks for the kiddos. Open to the community!\n\n11am – Egg Hunt #1\n12pm – Egg Hunt #2
