SUMMARY:Triskelee Farm Spring Market
DESCRIPTION:We hope to see you Saturday 28th for our Market! We’ll have some amazing vendors for adults and kids! Look for scrumptious treats\, massages\, face-painter\, locally made jewelry\, candles\, art\, and more. \nThe market is free to enter and shop. We’ll have farm to table food and drinks to purchase. Cousins Maine Lobster will be there from 11-3pm. \nPurchase tickets for a baby animal tour and see lambs\, a baby alpaca\, and the rest of our farm animals at 10 am or 1 pm. \nPurchase a kids pass to see the Easter bunny\, do an easy laid back egg hunt at your pace and time. Play on the bounce house and do a craft. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/triskelee-farm-spring-market/
LOCATION:Triskelee Farms\, 29700 SW Mountain Rd.\, West Linn\, Oregon\, 97068
CATEGORIES:Animals,Family Fun,Farm,Kids Calendar
